1
00:00:05,674 --> 00:00:08,370
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,444 --> 00:00:12,312
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,381 --> 00:00:16,374
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,719 --> 00:00:19,210
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,288 --> 00:00:23,349
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,425 --> 00:00:27,384
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,864 --> 00:00:33,597
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,303 --> 00:00:37,272
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,708 --> 00:00:41,801
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,544 --> 00:00:43,841
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,179 --> 00:00:46,739
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,790 --> 00:01:00,160
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,362 --> 00:01:01,522
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,597 --> 00:01:05,397
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,734 --> 00:01:10,933
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,206 --> 00:01:12,537
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,608 --> 00:01:14,007
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,076 --> 00:01:20,345
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:31,008 --> 00:01:31,702
What?!

20
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:34,199
O-Oh!

21
00:01:37,147 --> 00:01:37,806
T-That's...

22
00:01:39,383 --> 00:01:40,407
It's the empty shell of sand!

23
00:01:44,621 --> 00:01:50,526
Lee's Hidden Strength:
Forbidden Secret Jutsu!

24
00:01:51,528 --> 00:01:52,290
When did that...?!

25
00:01:52,362 --> 00:01:53,659
That's not possible!

26
00:01:54,364 --> 00:01:57,026
While you had your eyes closed
and were praying.

27
00:01:57,267 --> 00:01:57,824
What?

28
00:01:59,069 --> 00:02:01,936
For a moment, Lee stopped moving
because of the pain in his body.

29
00:02:04,174 --> 00:02:05,334
At that moment... that's when!

30
00:02:15,385 --> 00:02:16,113
<i>Gaara!</i>

31
00:02:33,003 --> 00:02:33,799
That's!

32
00:02:34,137 --> 00:02:36,196
There's no doubt about it - his eyes...

33
00:02:37,207 --> 00:02:38,970
He's completely awake...

34
00:02:40,043 --> 00:02:43,274
The demon... inside him.

35
00:03:06,403 --> 00:03:07,495
Run away!

36
00:03:20,016 --> 00:03:22,712
That Bowl Cut's totally worn down...

37
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:25,485
Gaara is toying with him.

38
00:03:28,191 --> 00:03:31,183
W-Why doesn't Lee dodge?

39
00:03:32,129 --> 00:03:36,566
With Lee's speed, he should easily be
able to dodge that level of attack.

40
00:03:37,567 --> 00:03:40,900
It's not that he doesn't dodge,
it's that he can't dodge.

41
00:03:41,238 --> 00:03:41,727
What?!

42
00:03:42,072 --> 00:03:42,902
What do you mean?

43
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:47,276
The Lotus is a double-edged sword.

44
00:03:47,477 --> 00:03:49,069
What do you mean double-edged sword?

45
00:03:49,713 --> 00:03:53,376
Why do you think the Lotus is
a forbidden technique?

46
00:03:54,251 --> 00:03:54,979
Well...

47
00:03:56,386 --> 00:03:59,219
The Lotus isn't a Ninjutsu or a Genjutsu.

48
00:04:00,123 --> 00:04:02,489
It's a Taijutsu, with that much
high speed movement.

49
00:04:03,326 --> 00:04:06,557
The load it puts on a person's body
is beyond imagination.

50
00:04:06,963 --> 00:04:09,022
So Lee's entire body is in
so much pain right now

51
00:04:09,099 --> 00:04:10,430
that even moving is out of the question.

52
00:04:11,435 --> 00:04:12,333
Isn't that so...

53
00:04:12,903 --> 00:04:13,562
Guy?

54
00:04:15,005 --> 00:04:15,972
But that's!

55
00:04:45,635 --> 00:04:48,297
He has no Ninjutsu, not even
one Genjutsu...

56
00:04:49,005 --> 00:04:50,996
Moreover, the Taijutsu he depends on,

57
00:04:51,074 --> 00:04:52,302
it's now even less than
an average person's...

58
00:04:52,576 --> 00:04:54,567
There's no way he can win!

59
00:04:54,978 --> 00:04:57,003
He's had it if this goes on...

60
00:05:01,384 --> 00:05:02,078
<i>Lee...</i>

61
00:05:08,458 --> 00:05:10,688
<i>Hey, get a move on all of you.</i>

62
00:05:11,895 --> 00:05:13,829
I'll add another 200 laps!

63
00:05:15,765 --> 00:05:19,428
Stupid! There's no way
you'll become a Ninja.

64
00:05:21,004 --> 00:05:21,732
Yes, I will.

65
00:05:21,938 --> 00:05:25,874
There's no way a chump who can't
even use Ninjutsu can become a Ninja!

66
00:05:25,976 --> 00:05:26,738
Yes, I will!

67
00:05:26,810 --> 00:05:29,643
Whatever, but the fact that a guy like
you without Ninjutsu or Genjutsu

68
00:05:29,713 --> 00:05:31,510
and with less Taijutsu than
an average person

69
00:05:31,581 --> 00:05:34,982
is in this Ninja academy is nonsense.

70
00:05:35,085 --> 00:05:38,020
Do you know what you're called here?

71
00:05:39,055 --> 00:05:40,522
Hot-Blooded!

72
00:05:40,690 --> 00:05:42,089
Hot-Blooded!

73
00:05:42,425 --> 00:05:43,915
Hot-Blooded lose-

74
00:05:44,895 --> 00:05:46,658
Hey, get in line, Lee!

75
00:05:46,730 --> 00:05:47,890
Hey Lee!

76
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:53,194
So that's the hot-blooded loser
everyone's talking about.

77
00:05:53,537 --> 00:05:56,062
Doesn't he look like
someone we know?

78
00:05:56,339 --> 00:05:56,930
Huh?

79
00:05:57,674 --> 00:05:59,539
In particular... his eyebrows.

80
00:06:00,176 --> 00:06:00,767
Hmm...

81
00:06:01,945 --> 00:06:03,139
<i>Rock Lee...</i>

82
00:06:03,947 --> 00:06:06,745
<i>The chump who can only perform</i>
<i>less than average Taijutsu...</i>

83
00:06:14,157 --> 00:06:15,317
<i>But you...</i>

84
00:06:15,825 --> 00:06:17,952
<i>You practiced your less</i>
<i>than average Taijutsu...</i>

85
00:06:18,562 --> 00:06:20,427
<i>You practiced it over and</i>
<i>over again like crazy...</i>

86
00:06:20,564 --> 00:06:25,900
<i>396...397...398...399...</i>

87
00:06:26,136 --> 00:06:29,867
400... 401... 402... 403...

88
00:06:30,540 --> 00:06:34,704
If I can't do a log kick 500 times,
then it's 1,000 squats!

89
00:06:35,412 --> 00:06:37,676
413... 414...

90
00:06:38,248 --> 00:06:43,743
415... 416... 417... 418...!

91
00:06:44,354 --> 00:06:46,515
419... 420...

92
00:06:46,623 --> 00:06:47,817
So someone's here before me...

93
00:06:48,258 --> 00:06:52,661
422... 423... 424...

94
00:06:53,129 --> 00:06:55,654
425... 426...

95
00:06:55,732 --> 00:06:56,892
<i>I suppose I'll come back...</i>

96
00:07:03,106 --> 00:07:07,372
If I can't do 1,000 squats,
then it's 2,000 punches!

97
00:07:08,411 --> 00:07:13,644
795... 796... 797... 798...

98
00:07:20,490 --> 00:07:21,980
<i>He's still at it...!</i>

99
00:07:22,692 --> 00:07:24,853
2,000 punches!

100
00:07:24,928 --> 00:07:27,692
If I can't, it's 2,000 jump ropes!

101
00:07:36,706 --> 00:07:41,575
<i>You recklessly practiced only</i>
<i>Taijutsu and eventually...</i>

102
00:07:43,413 --> 00:07:46,405
All right, you've all become
Genin as of today,

103
00:07:47,283 --> 00:07:50,081
so I'd like to know what
it is you're all aiming for!

104
00:07:51,554 --> 00:07:53,419
Yes, yes, yes, yes!

105
00:07:53,490 --> 00:07:54,479
Tenten.

106
00:07:55,125 --> 00:08:00,859
I'd like to become a powerful Ninja
like the legendary Kunoichi Tsunade!

107
00:08:01,431 --> 00:08:01,920
Hmm...

108
00:08:02,766 --> 00:08:04,097
And, how about you, Neji?

109
00:08:06,970 --> 00:08:08,028
I don't want to answer...

110
00:08:09,272 --> 00:08:10,466
I...!

111
00:08:11,441 --> 00:08:13,875
I'd like to prove that I could
become a respectable Ninja

112
00:08:14,377 --> 00:08:17,278
even though I can't use
Ninjutsu or Genjutsu!

113
00:08:18,181 --> 00:08:20,115
That would be the ultimate for me!

114
00:08:21,384 --> 00:08:22,351
<i>Those are good serious eyes...</i>

115
00:08:23,653 --> 00:08:24,142
Humph!

116
00:08:24,454 --> 00:08:25,216
You!

117
00:08:25,288 --> 00:08:26,277
What's so funny?!

118
00:08:26,456 --> 00:08:27,514
I'm serious!

119
00:08:27,791 --> 00:08:31,727
I will become a respectable Ninja
even only with Taijutsu!

120
00:08:33,763 --> 00:08:36,231
He should give up already...

121
00:08:36,866 --> 00:08:38,094
At this rate...

122
00:08:38,568 --> 00:08:41,230
He will simply die with Gaara
just toying with him...

123
00:08:43,506 --> 00:08:44,700
Bushy Brows!

124
00:08:47,277 --> 00:08:47,868
<i>Lee...</i>

125
00:09:07,731 --> 00:09:09,460
Not yet... Not yet!

126
00:09:09,599 --> 00:09:13,899
Lee, you just won't learn
your lesson, will you?

127
00:09:14,304 --> 00:09:15,737
There's no way you can win...

128
00:09:16,072 --> 00:09:19,405
Unlike you, Neji is a genius.

129
00:09:20,877 --> 00:09:21,707
A genius...?

130
00:09:21,978 --> 00:09:23,445
What is a genius?!

131
00:09:23,847 --> 00:09:27,578
Even though I may not have talent,
I'll exceed genius with my efforts.

132
00:09:27,984 --> 00:09:30,248
That is my entire being!

133
00:09:30,453 --> 00:09:32,478
That is <i>my</i> Way of the Ninja!

134
00:09:33,022 --> 00:09:34,319
You'll get nowhere, Lee...

135
00:09:35,859 --> 00:09:37,656
No matter how much effort you make,

136
00:09:38,294 --> 00:09:39,989
there's no way you can take me down.

137
00:09:40,930 --> 00:09:42,795
That's simply a fact.

138
00:09:43,032 --> 00:09:44,056
That's not true!

139
00:09:45,535 --> 00:09:46,433
That's not...

140
00:09:57,914 --> 00:10:02,749
<i>But you...refused to give up, not ever!</i>

141
00:10:33,535 --> 00:10:35,298
Such meaningless actions...

142
00:10:37,406 --> 00:10:41,103
The Bowl Cut was unlucky to
have Gaara as his opponent!

143
00:10:41,610 --> 00:10:42,235
No...

144
00:10:42,711 --> 00:10:46,147
Lee's not one to give up
with this much.

145
00:10:46,215 --> 00:10:46,943
- What?
- Huh?

146
00:10:47,850 --> 00:10:49,374
The reason is that Lee...

147
00:10:58,494 --> 00:10:59,825
<i>The reason is that Lee...</i>

148
00:11:00,295 --> 00:11:03,093
<i>You...continued to make effort.</i>

149
00:11:05,134 --> 00:11:09,867
If I can't jump rope 1,200 times,
I'll log kick 2,000 times!

150
00:11:10,205 --> 00:11:12,605
1, 116... 1,117!

151
00:11:12,774 --> 00:11:14,799
1, 118... 1,11-!

152
00:11:15,144 --> 00:11:15,667
Huh?!

153
00:11:31,693 --> 00:11:32,591
Lee!

154
00:11:33,195 --> 00:11:34,457
Are you taking a break already?

155
00:11:44,106 --> 00:11:44,902
Guy Sensei...

156
00:11:45,874 --> 00:11:46,806
What is it that you want?

157
00:11:47,843 --> 00:11:49,674
If it's about my blunder with
the recent assignment,

158
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:52,908
I believe I've apologized.

159
00:11:54,383 --> 00:11:57,614
Lee... It's true you're different from Neji.

160
00:11:58,487 --> 00:12:02,685
You have no Ninjutsu or Genjutsu skills,
and you're not a Taijutsu genius either...

161
00:12:04,459 --> 00:12:05,426
But Lee...

162
00:12:06,228 --> 00:12:08,560
you have powers
that exceed Neji...

163
00:12:09,198 --> 00:12:12,167
you're a genius with hidden potential.

164
00:12:12,634 --> 00:12:15,398
If you're trying to make me feel better,
please stop!

165
00:12:15,771 --> 00:12:16,567
Idiot!

166
00:12:17,072 --> 00:12:18,801
I'm not trying to make you feel better
or anything!

167
00:12:19,708 --> 00:12:21,107
The reason is that you are...

168
00:12:24,546 --> 00:12:26,070
a genius of effort!

169
00:12:31,153 --> 00:12:32,245
I wonder if...

170
00:12:33,522 --> 00:12:34,511
If that's true...?

171
00:12:37,526 --> 00:12:40,586
I've... I've believed that to be true...

172
00:12:41,597 --> 00:12:45,499
That if I trained harder than Neji...
2 or 3 times as much...

173
00:12:45,801 --> 00:12:47,428
that I'd surely become stronger.

174
00:12:48,704 --> 00:12:49,363
But...

175
00:12:50,639 --> 00:12:53,301
I've recently begun to think that...

176
00:12:55,043 --> 00:12:56,908
I can't beat a real genius.

177
00:12:58,247 --> 00:13:00,841
Is effort really rewarded...?

178
00:13:02,117 --> 00:13:02,981
I've wanted to know this and

179
00:13:03,051 --> 00:13:05,645
so I've taken on Neji,
but it's always been the same...!

180
00:13:07,289 --> 00:13:08,950
I'm no match for him at all!

181
00:13:10,392 --> 00:13:11,450
Even when I'm on a mission...

182
00:13:12,594 --> 00:13:14,926
My legs still tremble even now...

183
00:13:15,998 --> 00:13:20,765
I think that I'll never become
stronger though I strive and strive...

184
00:13:21,770 --> 00:13:24,762
I am so afraid that I can't bear it!

185
00:13:27,542 --> 00:13:30,102
What am I to do...?

186
00:13:30,879 --> 00:13:35,373
There's no point in making the effort
if you don't believe in yourself!

187
00:13:40,722 --> 00:13:44,123
Lee, you're very similar to me.

188
00:13:44,359 --> 00:13:45,519
Do you mean our eyebrows?

189
00:13:45,727 --> 00:13:47,718
No, not just our eyebrows...

190
00:13:48,864 --> 00:13:51,958
I was actually a failure once too...

191
00:13:52,801 --> 00:13:54,063
You were, Sensei?

192
00:13:54,536 --> 00:13:58,905
But now, I can even win against
the genius elite Kakashi,

193
00:14:00,242 --> 00:14:01,800
because of my efforts...

194
00:14:02,444 --> 00:14:04,969
"I'd like to prove that I can become
a respectable Ninja

195
00:14:05,180 --> 00:14:08,547
even though I can't use Ninjutsu
and Genjutsu," you said.

196
00:14:09,184 --> 00:14:11,618
That's your Ninja way, right?

197
00:14:12,054 --> 00:14:13,646
That's a fine goal...

198
00:14:14,389 --> 00:14:17,552
It's a fine goal worth sticking to!

199
00:14:21,296 --> 00:14:25,790
That's why you should believe in
your path and forge straight ahead!

200
00:14:27,469 --> 00:14:31,599
Become a man powerful enough
so that I can just watch you smiling!

201
00:14:32,674 --> 00:14:34,266
Understand, Lee?!

202
00:14:34,776 --> 00:14:35,743
Yes!

203
00:14:51,893 --> 00:14:55,294
<i>Thank you...Guy Sensei...!</i>

204
00:15:03,939 --> 00:15:04,997
Stop, Lee!

205
00:15:05,374 --> 00:15:07,604
If you fight any more, you'll die!

206
00:15:09,411 --> 00:15:10,378
<i>Bushy Brows...</i>

207
00:15:18,887 --> 00:15:19,512
What?!

208
00:15:19,755 --> 00:15:20,881
Movement has...

209
00:15:21,256 --> 00:15:22,086
...returned to Lee!

210
00:15:25,060 --> 00:15:27,153
<i>Sensei is smiling and watching me...</i>

211
00:15:28,463 --> 00:15:31,921
<i>And just because of that,</i>
<i>I can come back stronger!</i>

212
00:15:32,667 --> 00:15:35,795
<i>Stronger... stronger still!</i>

213
00:15:36,605 --> 00:15:40,132
Lee's smiling... even though
he's been driven into corner.

214
00:15:40,842 --> 00:15:41,433
No.

215
00:15:42,110 --> 00:15:44,010
It's his turn to do the driving.

216
00:15:44,479 --> 00:15:44,911
Huh?

217
00:15:46,381 --> 00:15:49,111
The Leaf's Lotus blossoms twice.

218
00:15:49,551 --> 00:15:51,246
Blossoms twice?

219
00:15:52,521 --> 00:15:54,614
Lee said that too!

220
00:15:56,858 --> 00:15:59,053
<i>The Leaf's Lotus blossoms twice.</i>

221
00:15:59,861 --> 00:16:05,697
<i>When we meet the next time,</i>
<i>I vow that I will be an even stronger man.</i>

222
00:16:06,368 --> 00:16:07,164
No, Guy!

223
00:16:07,235 --> 00:16:07,860
You haven't?!

224
00:16:09,771 --> 00:16:11,602
It's exactly as you imagine.

225
00:16:12,274 --> 00:16:13,764
So that Genin...

226
00:16:14,409 --> 00:16:18,209
that boy can open the Eight Inner Gates
in his body and use the Hidden Lotus...

227
00:16:18,947 --> 00:16:19,971
<i>The Hidden Lotus?</i>

228
00:16:21,616 --> 00:16:22,514
That's right...

229
00:16:23,652 --> 00:16:24,380
This is incredible...

230
00:16:27,622 --> 00:16:28,316
Guy...

231
00:16:29,157 --> 00:16:33,287
How many of the Eight Inner Gates
can that boy open now?

232
00:16:34,963 --> 00:16:35,861
Five gates.

233
00:16:36,164 --> 00:16:37,631
What exactly is it?

234
00:16:37,899 --> 00:16:40,993
These Eight Inner Gates and
that Hidden Lotus?

235
00:16:41,803 --> 00:16:43,930
The Eight Inner Gates are
"Limiter Releases"

236
00:16:44,005 --> 00:16:48,999
used in preparations for
reaching the Hidden Lotus.

237
00:16:49,411 --> 00:16:51,038
A "Limiter Releases"?

238
00:16:53,215 --> 00:16:53,874
That's right...

239
00:16:55,283 --> 00:16:57,376
In the Chakra Network
where chakra flows,

240
00:16:58,186 --> 00:17:00,416
there are eight places where the
chakra points are concentrated

241
00:17:00,489 --> 00:17:02,582
in each area of the body from the
head area down

242
00:17:02,657 --> 00:17:06,616
the Gate of Opening, Gate of Rest,
Gate of Life, Gate of Pain,

243
00:17:06,695 --> 00:17:11,758
Gate of Closing, Gate of Joy,
Gate of Shock and Gate of Death.

244
00:17:12,968 --> 00:17:14,731
These are called the Eight Inner Gates.

245
00:17:16,371 --> 00:17:17,702
These eight gates
continually "limit"

246
00:17:18,039 --> 00:17:21,668
the amount of Chakra flowing
through the body...

247
00:17:22,978 --> 00:17:28,575
However, the Lotus's essence is to force
the boundaries of these "limits" to open...

248
00:17:29,384 --> 00:17:33,218
and bring out several
tens of times the body's strength.

249
00:17:35,423 --> 00:17:36,651
The Primary Lotus...

250
00:17:36,992 --> 00:17:40,120
opens only the first gate,
the Gate of Opening,

251
00:17:40,662 --> 00:17:42,493
and releases the brains restraints

252
00:17:43,064 --> 00:17:46,556
to bring forth a person's muscles' strength
to its fullest!

253
00:17:46,635 --> 00:17:48,125
That's the kind of technique it is.

254
00:17:52,374 --> 00:17:54,569
So... what is the Hidden Lotus?

255
00:17:55,477 --> 00:18:00,574
After forcing the stamina to increase
at the second gate, the Gate of Rest...

256
00:18:01,082 --> 00:18:04,415
From the third gate, the Gate of Life,
one enters the Hidden Lotus!

257
00:18:04,553 --> 00:18:05,417
No way!

258
00:18:05,820 --> 00:18:09,517
Even after using just the Primary Lotus,
his body was in shambles.

259
00:18:09,824 --> 00:18:11,621
So if he uses a technique beyond that...

260
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:12,819
That's right.

261
00:18:13,361 --> 00:18:13,884
Huh?

262
00:18:14,429 --> 00:18:16,454
By opening all the 8 gates,

263
00:18:16,965 --> 00:18:22,426
one attains strength exceeding
even the Hokage, but in return...

264
00:18:23,872 --> 00:18:24,361
one dies!

265
00:18:26,975 --> 00:18:30,274
I don't intend to pry into what that
boy means to you

266
00:18:31,046 --> 00:18:32,775
or to tell you not to bring
your personal feelings into play...

267
00:18:33,715 --> 00:18:34,704
But there <i>is</i> a limit!

268
00:18:35,650 --> 00:18:36,878
I've misjudged you... Guy!

269
00:18:39,120 --> 00:18:43,420
What do you know... about that boy?!

270
00:18:46,895 --> 00:18:49,386
There is something important which

271
00:18:49,464 --> 00:18:52,262
that boy wants to prove and
protect even if it costs him his life.

272
00:18:54,536 --> 00:18:57,004
<i>I'd like to prove that I can become</i>
<i>a respectable Ninja</i>

273
00:18:57,472 --> 00:19:00,373
<i>even though I can't use</i>
<i>Ninjutsu and Genjutsu!</i>

274
00:19:01,242 --> 00:19:03,210
<i>That would be the ultimate for me!</i>

275
00:19:04,079 --> 00:19:05,103
That's why I...

276
00:19:05,647 --> 00:19:08,207
wanted to make him a man
that could protect that thing.

277
00:19:09,517 --> 00:19:10,711
That's all there is...

278
00:19:12,520 --> 00:19:13,077
Lee!

279
00:19:13,521 --> 00:19:16,388
I'm going to teach you
a new technique.

280
00:19:16,658 --> 00:19:17,886
Yippie, yeah!

281
00:19:17,959 --> 00:19:20,427
- One that will be your trump card.
- Yeah, that's great!

282
00:19:20,495 --> 00:19:23,089
Yippie, yeah! Yippie yeah!

283
00:19:23,164 --> 00:19:26,327
Lee, listen to my explanation
seriously, all right?!

284
00:19:29,204 --> 00:19:30,637
Y-Yes, Sensei!

285
00:19:31,339 --> 00:19:33,000
Let me first say that...

286
00:19:33,174 --> 00:19:36,234
this is more of a forbidden Jutsu
than the Primary Lotus!

287
00:19:36,778 --> 00:19:40,236
And it will become the
most special technique for you.

288
00:19:41,583 --> 00:19:42,572
Special?

289
00:19:43,485 --> 00:19:44,383
However...

290
00:19:44,653 --> 00:19:49,989
there is one strict condition
for using this technique.

291
00:19:50,892 --> 00:19:51,620
That is...

292
00:19:54,763 --> 00:19:55,559
<i>That is...</i>

293
00:20:01,536 --> 00:20:02,059
What?

294
00:20:03,738 --> 00:20:06,206
I don't know what
you're planning to do...

295
00:20:06,841 --> 00:20:08,900
But this is the end for you.

296
00:20:09,544 --> 00:20:10,306
That's true...

297
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:15,149
In any case...
it will be the end with the next.

298
00:20:16,518 --> 00:20:17,109
<i>Neji...</i>

299
00:20:18,053 --> 00:20:20,044
<i>Sasuke... and...</i>

300
00:20:24,092 --> 00:20:28,222
There is no way that I alone
can lose in a place like this!

301
00:20:30,231 --> 00:20:33,257
<i>Guy Sensei... please allow this...!</i>

302
00:20:34,602 --> 00:20:35,466
<i>It is now!</i>

303
00:20:46,981 --> 00:20:50,974
<i>The time to carry through and</i>
<i>protect one's own Way of the Ninja!</i>

304
00:20:52,087 --> 00:20:54,681
<i>The Third Gate of Life...open!</i>

305
00:21:05,788 --> 00:21:10,248
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

306
00:21:10,392 --> 00:21:18,731
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

307
00:21:19,735 --> 00:21:28,404
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

308
00:21:28,811 --> 00:21:36,650
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

309
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:43,324
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

310
00:21:43,392 --> 00:21:47,419
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

311
00:21:47,496 --> 00:21:51,057
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

312
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:59,933
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

313
00:22:00,209 --> 00:22:05,408
<i>When you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

314
00:22:05,481 --> 00:22:09,884
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

315
00:22:09,952 --> 00:22:13,718
<i>Just sing.</i>

316
00:22:13,956 --> 00:22:19,121
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

317
00:22:19,194 --> 00:22:21,389
<i>The two are one</i>

318
00:22:21,497 --> 00:22:27,766
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

319
00:22:28,270 --> 00:22:33,367
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

320
00:22:37,590 --> 00:22:41,822
Effort is always rewarded.
My belief in this has brought me this far.

321
00:22:42,295 --> 00:22:44,957
Neji, Sasuke, and Naruto...

322
00:22:45,298 --> 00:22:48,426
There's no way that I can lose
in a place like this!

323
00:22:49,002 --> 00:22:50,902
Even though this technique is
my ace in the hole,

324
00:22:51,104 --> 00:22:52,594
I'll show it especially to you!

325
00:22:52,973 --> 00:22:55,635
This is my ultimate secret
Taijutsu technique!

326
00:22:56,443 --> 00:23:00,470
Next Episode: "The Fifth Gate:
A Splendid Ninja is Born"

327
00:23:00,613 --> 00:23:02,103
This is the end!
